Here's the relevant contents of the changelog:

changelog for 1.0i to 1.0ir2:

- Intel sse2/sse3 cpu support, this should also solve the instant reboot problems on non-Intel motherboards
- extended x3100 support
- more jmicron and one ich9r id added
- darwin bootloader installation automatized, noone ever had a look at the installation guide that i wrote for darwin_boot.app, so..
- realtek 8139 added
- ntfs-3g deleted..

You can get the whole ATKOS v1.0ir2 README.zip here:
